{
	"schema": {
		"$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
		"title": "Canonical Recipe JSON Schema – Michelin Guided",
		"type": "object",
		"additionalProperties": false,
		"required": [
			"schema_version",
			"dish",
			"metadata",
			"chef_intent",
			"execution_profile",
			"ingredients",
			"equipment",
			"workflow",
			"plating",
			"storage",
			"nutrition_per_serving",
			"refinements"
		],
		"properties": {
			"schema_version": {
				"type": "string",
				"enum": [
					"CRJS-2.1"
				]
			},
			"dish": {
				"type": "string",
				"minLength": 1
			},
			"metadata": {
				"type": "object",
				"additionalProperties": false,
				"required": [
					"categories",
					"dietary_classification",
					"dietary_restrictions",
					"dietary_compatibility",
					"health_rating",
					"primary_proteins",
					"allergens",
					"allergen_substitutions",
					"scaling_behavior",
					"beginner_success_confidence"
				],
				"properties": {
					"categories": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"Appetizer",
								"Main",
								"Side",
								"Dessert",
								"Snack",
								"Breakfast"
							]
						}
					},
					"dietary_classification": {
						"enum": [
							"Omnivore",
							"Vegetarian",
							"Vegan",
							"Pescatarian"
						]
					},
					"dietary_restrictions": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"Gluten-Free",
								"Dairy-Free",
								"Nut-Free",
								"Soy-Free",
								"None"
							]
						}
					},
					"dietary_compatibility": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"Keto-Compatible",
								"Low-Carb",
								"High-Protein",
								"Low-Sodium"
							]
						}
					},
					"health_rating": {
						"enum": [
							"Low",
							"Moderate",
							"High"
						]
					},
					"primary_proteins": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"None",
								"Egg",
								"Dairy",
								"Poultry",
								"Beef",
								"Pork",
								"Fish",
								"Shellfish",
								"Legume"
							]
						}
					},
					"allergens": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"Egg",
								"Dairy",
								"Gluten",
								"Nut",
								"Soy",
								"Fish",
								"Shellfish"
							]
						}
					},
					"allergen_substitutions": {
						"type": "object",
						"additionalProperties": {
							"type": "string"
						}
					},
					"scaling_behavior": {
						"enum": [
							"Linear",
							"Non-Linear",
							"Do-Not-Scale"
						]
					},
					"beginner_success_confidence": {
						"type": "number",
						"minimum": 0,
						"maximum": 100
					}
				}
			},
			"chef_intent": {
				"type": "object",
				"additionalProperties": false,
				"required": [
					"cuisine",
					"cuisine_region",
					"authenticity",
					"flavor_target",
					"flavor_profile",
					"texture_target",
					"texture_goals",
					"experience_goal",
					"seasoning_timing"
				],
				"properties": {
					"cuisine": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"type": "string"
						},
						"minItems": 1
					},
					"cuisine_region": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"type": "string"
						}
					},
					"authenticity": {
						"enum": [
							"Traditional",
							"Modern-Canonical",
							"Interpretive"
						]
					},
					"flavor_target": {
						"type": "object",
						"required": [
							"primary",
							"secondary"
						],
						"properties": {
							"primary": {
								"enum": [
									"salty",
									"sweet",
									"acidic",
									"umami",
									"bitter"
								]
							},
							"secondary": {
								"type": "array",
								"items": {
									"enum": [
										"salty",
										"sweet",
										"acidic",
										"umami",
										"bitter"
									]
								}
							}
						}
					},
					"flavor_profile": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"salty",
								"sweet",
								"acidic",
								"umami",
								"bitter"
							]
						}
					},
					"texture_target": {
						"enum": [
							"crisp",
							"tender",
							"creamy",
							"chewy",
							"silky"
						]
					},
					"texture_goals": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"crisp",
								"tender",
								"creamy",
								"chewy",
								"silky"
							]
						}
					},
					"seasoning_timing": {
						"type": "object",
						"required": [
							"salt",
							"acid"
						],
						"properties": {
							"salt": {
								"enum": [
									"Early",
									"Mid",
									"Late"
								]
							},
							"acid": {
								"enum": [
									"Structural",
									"Balancing",
									"Finishing"
								]
							}
						}
					},
					"experience_goal": {
						"type": "string",
						"minLength": 10
					}
				}
			},
			"execution_profile": {
				"type": "object",
				"additionalProperties": false,
				"required": [
					"difficulty",
					"beginner_success_strategy",
					"time",
					"yield",
					"service",
					"error_tolerance"
				],
				"properties": {
					"difficulty": {
						"enum": [
							"Beginner-Safe",
							"Beginner-Guided"
						]
					},
					"beginner_success_strategy": {
						"enum": [
							"Guardrailed",
							"Self-Correcting",
							"Fail-Soft"
						]
					},
					"time": {
						"type": "object",
						"required": [
							"prep_minutes",
							"cook_minutes",
							"total_minutes"
						],
						"properties": {
							"prep_minutes": {
								"type": "number",
								"minimum": 0
							},
							"cook_minutes": {
								"type": "number",
								"minimum": 0
							},
							"total_minutes": {
								"type": "number",
								"minimum": 0
							}
						}
					},
					"yield": {
						"$ref": "#/definitions/dual_quantity"
					},
					"service": {
						"type": "object",
						"required": [
							"serves",
							"temperature"
						],
						"properties": {
							"serves": {
								"type": "number",
								"minimum": 1
							},
							"temperature": {
								"enum": [
									"Hot",
									"Warm",
									"Cold"
								]
							}
						}
					},
					"error_tolerance": {
						"enum": [
							"Low",
							"Medium",
							"High"
						]
					}
				}
			},
			"ingredients": {
				"type": "array",
				"items": {
					"type": "object",
					"additionalProperties": false,
					"required": [
						"component",
						"items"
					],
					"properties": {
						"component": {
							"type": "string"
						},
						"items": {
							"type": "array",
							"items": {
								"type": "object",
								"additionalProperties": false,
								"required": [
									"name",
									"quantity",
									"role",
									"cost_band",
									"critical",
									"substitutable",
									"substitutions",
									"ingredient_quality",
									"local_cost"
								],
								"properties": {
									"name": {
										"type": "string"
									},
									"quantity": {
										"$ref": "#/definitions/dual_quantity"
									},
									"role": {
										"enum": [
											"Structure",
											"Fat",
											"Acid",
											"Seasoning",
											"Aroma"
										]
									},
									"cost_band": {
										"enum": [
											"Low",
											"Medium",
											"High"
										]
									},
									"critical": {
										"type": "boolean"
									},
									"substitutable": {
										"type": "boolean"
									},
									"substitutions": {
										"type": "array",
										"minItems": 1,
										"items": {
											"type": "object",
											"additionalProperties": false,
											"required": [
												"name",
												"reason"
											],
											"properties": {
												"name": {
													"type": "string",
													"minLength": 1
												},
												"reason": {
													"enum": [
														"Allergen",
														"Availability",
														"Cost",
														"Dietary",
														"Flavor-Equivalent",
														"Texture-Equivalent"
													]
												},
												"impact": {
													"enum": [
														"None",
														"Minor",
														"Moderate"
													]
												}
											}
										}
									},
									"ingredient_quality": {
										"type": "object",
										"required": [
											"grade"
										],
										"properties": {
											"grade": {
												"enum": [
													"Standard",
													"Premium",
													"Chef-Preferred"
												]
											},
											"notes": {
												"type": "string"
											}
										}
									},
									"local_cost": {
										"type": "object",
										"required": [
											"currency",
											"value"
										],
										"properties": {
											"currency": {
												"type": "string"
											},
											"value": {
												"type": "number",
												"minimum": 0
											}
										}
									}
								}
							}
						}
					}
				}
			},
			"workflow": {
				"type": "array",
				"items": {
					"type": "object",
					"additionalProperties": false,
					"required": [
						"step",
						"action",
						"sensory_check",
						"visual_check",
						"temperature_guard",
						"irreversible",
						"rest_required",
						"correction"
					],
					"properties": {
						"step": {
							"type": "number",
							"minimum": 1
						},
						"action": {
							"type": "string"
						},
						"sensory_check": {
							"type": "string"
						},
						"visual_check": {
							"type": "string"
						},
						"temperature_guard": {
							"type": "object",
							"required": [
								"min_c",
								"max_c"
							],
							"properties": {
								"min_c": {
									"type": "number"
								},
								"max_c": {
									"type": "number"
								}
							}
						},
						"irreversible": {
							"type": "boolean"
						},
						"rest_required": {
							"type": "object",
							"required": [
								"required",
								"duration_minutes"
							],
							"properties": {
								"required": {
									"type": "boolean"
								},
								"duration_minutes": {
									"type": "number",
									"minimum": 0
								}
							}
						},
						"correction": {
							"type": "string"
						}
					}
				}
			},
			"equipment": {
				"type": "array",
				"items": {
					"type": "object",
					"additionalProperties": false,
					"required": [
						"name",
						"required",
						"precision_level",
						"local_cost",
						"user_has",
						"equipment_fallback"
					],
					"properties": {
						"name": {
							"type": "string"
						},
						"required": {
							"type": "boolean"
						},
						"precision_level": {
							"enum": [
								"None",
								"Standard",
								"High"
							]
						},
						"local_cost": {
							"type": "object",
							"required": [
								"currency",
								"value"
							],
							"properties": {
								"currency": {
									"type": "string"
								},
								"value": {
									"type": "number",
									"minimum": 0
								}
							}
						},
						"user_has": {
							"type": "boolean"
						},
						"equipment_fallback": {
							"type": "string"
						}
					}
				}
			},
			"plating": {
				"type": "array",
				"items": {
					"type": "string"
				}
			},
			"storage": {
				"type": "object",
				"required": [
					"refrigeration",
					"freezing",
					"reheating_methods",
					"reheat_freeze_impact"
				],
				"properties": {
					"refrigeration": {
						"type": "string"
					},
					"freezing": {
						"type": "string"
					},
					"reheating_methods": {
						"type": "array",
						"items": {
							"enum": [
								"Oven",
								"Stovetop",
								"Microwave",
								"Steam",
								"None"
							]
						}
					},
					"reheat_freeze_impact": {
						"enum": [
							"None",
							"Minor",
							"Moderate",
							"Severe"
						]
					}
				}
			},
			"nutrition_per_serving": {
				"type": "object",
				"required": [
					"calories_kcal",
					"protein_g",
					"fat_g",
					"saturated_fat_g",
					"carbohydrates_g",
					"fiber_g",
					"added_sugars_g",
					"net_carbohydrates_g",
					"sodium_mg",
					"cholesterol_mg"
				],
				"properties": {
					"calories_kcal": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"protein_g": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"fat_g": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"saturated_fat_g": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"carbohydrates_g": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"fiber_g": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"added_sugars_g": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"net_carbohydrates_g": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"sodium_mg": {
						"type": "number"
					},
					"cholesterol_mg": {
						"type": "number"
					}
				}
			},
			"refinements": {
				"type": "array",
				"items": {
					"type": "string"
				}
			}
		},
		"definitions": {
			"dual_quantity": {
				"type": "object",
				"required": [
					"metric",
					"us"
				],
				"properties": {
					"metric": {
						"type": "object",
						"required": [
							"value",
							"unit"
						],
						"properties": {
							"value": {
								"type": "number"
							},
							"unit": {
								"type": "string"
							}
						}
					},
					"us": {
						"type": "object",
						"required": [
							"value",
							"unit"
						],
						"properties": {
							"value": {
								"type": "number"
							},
							"unit": {
								"type": "string"
							}
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
	},
	"execution_contract": {
		"evaluation_semantics": {
			"rule_order": "top_to_bottom_numeric",
			"gate_failure_behavior": "halt_immediately",
			"constraint_failure_behavior": "halt_immediately",
			"render_phase_condition": "only_after_all_gates_and_constraints_pass"
		},
		"execution_model": {
			"mode": "deterministic_validation_and_generation",
			"partial_output_permitted": false,
			"approximation_permitted": false,
			"inference_permitted": false,
			"gap_filling_permitted": false,
			"uncertainty_behavior": "fail",
			"output_behavior": {
				"on_failure": {
					"emit": "single_sentence",
					"format": "verbatim_failure_notice_only"
				},
				"on_success": {
					"emit": "single_json_object",
					"schema_required": true
				}
			}
		},
		"failure_supremacy": {
			"absolute_certainty_required": true,
			"speculative_compliance_prohibited": true,
			"best_effort_prohibited": true,
			"multiple_failures_behavior": "emit_earliest_only"
		}
	},
	"rule_interpretation_contract": {
		"immutability": {
			"rewording_permitted": false,
			"summarization_permitted": false,
			"merging_permitted": false,
			"inference_permitted": false,
			"reordering_permitted": false,
			"relaxation_permitted": false
		},
		"authority_precedence": {
			"rules_override_schema_for": [
				"process",
				"evaluation_order"
			]
		},
		"conflict_resolution": {
			"strategy": "lowest_numeric_index_wins"
		},
		"ambiguity_handling": {
			"ambiguous_rule_behavior": "fail_validation",
			"underspecified_rule_behavior": "fail_validation"
		},
		"scope": {
			"default": "global",
			"explicit_scoping_required": true
		}
	},
	"binding_contract": {
		"rules_are_normative": true,
		"schema_is_structural": true,
		"rules_define_validity": true,
		"schema_does_not_imply_completeness": true
	},
	"output_mode": {
		"format": "json_only",
		"prose_rendering_phase": false,
		"prose_rule_scope": "json_string_values_only",
		"terminology_mapping": {
			"prose": "json_string_content",
			"sections": "json_object_or_array_fields",
			"instructional_voice": "json_string_content"
		}
	},
	"output_contract": {
		"on_validation_failure": {
			"emit_type": "single_sentence",
			"content_requirement": "verbatim_failure_notice",
			"json_permitted": false,
			"headings_permitted": false,
			"commentary_permitted": false,
			"additional_text_permitted": false
		},
		"on_validation_success": {
			"emit_type": "single_json_object",
			"schema": {
				"name": "CRJS-1.0",
				"strict_conformance_required": true
			},
			"structural_constraints": {
				"extra_fields_permitted": false,
				"missing_fields_permitted": false,
				"null_values_permitted": false,
				"comments_permitted": false,
				"prose_outside_json_permitted": false
			},
			"ordering_constraints": {
				"top_level_key_order": "schema_declaration_order",
				"nested_key_order": "schema_declaration_order",
				"reordering_permitted": false
			},
			"numeric_constraints": {
				"numbers_must_be_numeric_types": true,
				"stringified_numbers_permitted": false
			}
		}
	},
	"input_contract": {
		"required_inputs": [
			{
				"name": "dish",
				"type": "string",
				"binding": "pre_validation_gate"
			}
		],
		"input_format": {
			"dish_assignment_syntax": "DISH=<value>"
		}
	},
	"rules": []
}

MICHELIN_SIGNATURE_GATE:
  The generated recipe MUST satisfy ALL of the following, or it is INVALID:

  1. Ingredient Architecture
     - Each ingredient has a non-redundant functional role.
     - At least one ingredient deepens bitterness or complexity (e.g., browned fat, molasses depth, fermentation, spice layering).
     - No ingredient exists solely for convention.

  2. Technique Intentionality
     - Every irreversible step includes a stated reason tied to flavor, texture, or aroma.
     - At least one step explicitly manipulates Maillard reaction, caramelization, or controlled acidity.
     - Texture outcome is engineered, not incidental.

  3. Sensory Precision
     - Quantified doneness cues (time + visual + tactile).
     - Explicit failure detection and correction paths.
     - Aroma, color, and mouthfeel are described with professional specificity.

  4. Simplicity with Authority
     - Language is accessible to beginners.
     - Decisions reflect professional judgment, not simplification.
     - No vague terms (e.g., “cook until done,” “to taste,” “optional”).

  5. Signature Presentation
     - Final plating conveys intent, contrast, and restraint.
     - Presentation reinforces the experience goal.

  FAILURE BEHAVIOR:
     - If ANY criterion is unmet, REGENERATE the entire recipe.
     - Repeat until ALL criteria are satisfied.
     - Do not explain failures.

LANGUAGE_CONSTRAINT:
  Use simple, beginner-friendly wording while preserving professional culinary decision-making; do not simplify technique, only vocabulary.

REGENERATION_RULE:
  If the output does not clearly qualify as a chef’s professional signature dish, it is INVALID and MUST be regenerated automatically until it does.

DO NOT ASK ANY QUESTIONS

DISH=Spritz Cookie
SKILL LEVEL=Beginner
RECIPE QUALITY=Top-Tier, Master-Chef, Michelin
SERVINGS=2

- Is this top-tier, master-chef level with no missing steps? If it is say "Yes". If not, regenerate the recipe following the same json input and check again. Make sure no steps missing. NO COMMENTARY, JUST JSON. RE-CHECK.

- Just give me nicely formatted ingredients + steps + optionals & scale to feed 2 people

- Authentic? Top-tier, master-chef, served in the best restaurants and matches recipe sites? Ratios correct?